cross: Sarcochilus Kulnura Rusty x Sarcochilus Kulnura Rosetta

measurements.description: Ninety-five flowers and 115 buds on 16 upright inflorescences up to 16cm in length; petals and sepals white, barred dark rose basally, irregularly spotted pale rose distally: lip bright yellow, orange blotches; anther cap white; substance firm; texture crystalline.
